  <brief_title>Comparison of Harmonic Scalpel to Conventional Diathermy in Perforator Flap Elevation for Head and Neck Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Randomised, Single-blinded Study : Comparison of Harmonic Scalpel to Conventional Diathermy in Perforator Flap</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Samsung Medical Center</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Samsung Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to compare the efficacy of Harmonic Scalpel with conventional diathermy
      technique in terms of reducing elevation time and perioperative complications of perforator
      flaps for head and neck reconstruction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
